Name: Spaceflux
About the game: Spaceflux is an online shooter where the map is an infinite loop. Going to the center takes you back to where you started. Learn to navigate fractal worlds in hyper-fast arena combat. Master the 6 IMPOSSIBLE GEOMETRIES to take your shooter skills to the next level. FRACTAL SPACE HORIZONTAL LOOP - the map repeats endlessly in all directions. VERTICAL LOOP - fall forever. FRACTAL MINIMAP - there is a miniature version of the map inside this building that you can jump into and come back to the same place. MIRROR MODE - the map is mirrored and so are you. PORTALS FULLY DESTRUCTIBLE MAPS Join us on Discord for quick matchmaking!
